org.teatrove.trove.util
Interface MergedClass.InvocationEventObserver

Enclosing class:
MergedClass
public static interface MergedClass.InvocationEventObserver

Instances of the InvocationEventObserver can optionally be passed as a parameter to an overloaded MergedClass constructor. A class external to MergedClass should implement this interface to act as a (GoF) mediator for collecting elapsed time information.
